bug.short_desc: Mediawriter shows a ever changing size of USB device
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1232862 Screen video of Fedora Media Writer
Description of problem: The size of USB device is show as EB (Exobytes?) and doesn't stop changing.
What is it? freesize? total size?
Please consult video

Hello Johannes, thank you for the report. I've got multiple people complaining about their SD card readers reporting insane sizes while there is actually no memory card inserted. I'm definitely going to look into this problem soon.
